---
// FeeStructure.astro — Homepage fee section
// Private MVP: no specific percentages shown publicly
---

<section id="fees" class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-[#0d1117]">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12 max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-white/30 text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Fee Structure</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">
        Performance-Aligned Fees
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
        Our fee model is designed so we only win when you win.
        Early participants in the private phase receive preferential terms.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Fee principles -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10">

      <!-- Management fee -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/4 border border-white/10 p-8">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 mb-4">Management Fee</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/40 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Annual fee on assets under management. Covers infrastructure, strategy
          development, monitoring, and investor reporting.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/40">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-teal-400">&#10003;</span>
            Accrued daily, settled at period end
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-teal-400">&#10003;</span>
            0% during paper trading period
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-teal-400">&#10003;</span>
            Competitive vs. market standard
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Performance fee -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-accent-500/5 border border-accent-500/20 p-8">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 mb-4">Performance Fee <span class="text-accent-400/60 text-xs font-normal">+ High-Water Mark</span></div>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/40 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Charged only on net profits above the high-water mark. If the portfolio declines,
          no performance fee is charged until the previous peak is recovered.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/40">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-400">&#10003;</span>
            High-watermark: no double-charging on recoveries
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-400">&#10003;</span>
            Below industry standard
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-400">&#10003;</span>
            Only on net gains &mdash; losses reduce the base
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- No withdrawal fee / No lock-up -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-10">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/2 p-5 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70 font-medium">No Withdrawal Fee</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/35">Withdraw your capital without penalty.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/2 p-5 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0">&#10003;</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70 font-medium">No Lock-Up</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/35">No mandatory lock-up period for your capital.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA callout -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-teal-500/20 bg-teal-500/5 p-5">
      <div class="text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m11.25 11.25.041-.02a.75.75 0 0 1 1.063.852l-.708 2.836a.75.75 0 0 0 1.063.853l.041-.021M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Zm-9-3.75h.008v.008H12V8.25Z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/50">
        Fee details are discussed individually during onboarding.
        <a href="/fees" class="text-accent-400/70 hover:text-accent-400 underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">Learn more about our fee structure</a>
        or <a href="mailto:yuriycooleshov@gmail.com" class="text-accent-400/70 hover:text-accent-400 underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">get in touch</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
